{"tid":2081740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發唔發覺真係唔應該屌公務員？","createTime":"2020-06-27T12:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T16:50:07.000Z","uid":235021,"like":15,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f89dee65247d929bd9d2dfa83f7bcd5b63de59","tid":2081740,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"公務員嘅福利人工七八嘅打工仔都冇，屌佢哋班人多數揾萬幾蚊（香港一半打工仔人工冇兩萬），最多三四萬，永遠都唔會好似佢哋咁做admin work 都頂薪三四萬。<br />\n<br />\n屌佢哋嘅人唔明如果佢哋講政治野分分鐘冇左個飯碗，而佢哋可能都供緊樓，準備緊結婚，唔可以冇左個收入。所以屌佢哋之前都要諗下佢哋都係揾飯食，唔可以話叫人為左啲短期內冇乜可能實現嘅理念放棄份好工。"},{"pid":"da2ab9b1bdd57c918c424d3fd57b33646b017942","tid":2081740,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"巴打公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帽員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd429381ddf1282966c1aff7a7d48c6610658e52","tid":2081740,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"da2ab9b1bdd57c918c424d3fd57b33646b017942","tid":2081740,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"巴打公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帽員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"唔係，只係公道講句說話"},{"pid":"09558fb20bb1e17a2cb933d4a97deeff91437b4c","tid":2081740,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd429381ddf1282966c1aff7a7d48c6610658e52","tid":2081740,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"da2ab9b1bdd57c918c424d3fd57b33646b017942","tid":2081740,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:52:05.000Z","msg":"巴打公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帽員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.g